### FR-08 Checkout — Step 3 smoke (TC-08-001 / ER-08-001)
### Captured post-hoc as documentation of what was actually executed via curl (Model C).
### Not built up-front; not a test runner.

### 1. Login as test user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@eshop.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

### 2. Seed cart to real total X = 30,000,000 VND
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max",
  "price": 30000000,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 3. Confirm cart state before checkout
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Checkout with forged total_amount = 1 (input under test)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "total_amount": 1,
  "shipping_address": "123 Le Loi, TP.HCM"
}

### 5. Read back the persisted order (actual, no expected encoded here)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders/my-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Read back the persisted order by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders/1
